    <!-- cd-product-intro -->
    <div id="cd-product-tour">
      <ul>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-active right-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Create Lists</h2>
            <p>Create a Lytit List of locations and receive a live feed of their real-time social media activity. The moment something happens, you'll be in the loop!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div>
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/list@2x.png" data-video="/assets/open_list" alt="List Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-not-visible cd-move-right left-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Share & Join Lists</h2>
            <p>Discover new places through the Lists of others. Where to read a book? What are the best street fairs in Tokyo? No matter what you're looking for, there's probably a List that can help!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div>
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/find_list@2x.png" data-video="/assets/find_list" alt="Find Lists Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-not-visible cd-move-right right-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Browse the World</h2>
            <p>Use the Lyt Map to browse what's going on at places and areas from all around the world.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: -40px">Found a cool spot? Add it to a List to enlyten others of your discovery.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div>
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/place_search@2x.png" data-video="/assets/place_search" alt="Lyt Map Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cd-single-item cd-not-visible cd-move-right left-floater">
          <div class="cd-caption">
            <h2>Search Live</h2>
            <p>Whether it's a rock concert, a pair of YEEZYs or dogs, the Live Search will show you places where you can find them at this instance!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cd-image-container">
            <div>
              <div class="cd-phone-frame"></div>
              <div class="cd-image-wrapper">
                <img src="/assets/live_search@2x.png" data-video="/assets/live_search" alt="Live Search Preview">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
